10149:  9: - docs + business
10150: 10: 
10151: 11: Process:
10152: 12: 
10153: 13: 1. Query each memory
10154: 14: 2. Extract relevant signals
10155: 15: 3. Merge into unified response
10156: 16: 4. If source is code, resolve symbols via CodeGraph before broad file reads
10157: 17: 5. Register reusable pattern in code-memory feedback loop
