10861: <file path="optimization/examples/sla-query.md">
10862:  1: # Example: SLA Query
10863:  2: 
10864:  3: ## Input
10865:  4: 
10866:  5: Que dice el SLA.
10867:  6: 
10868:  7: ## Ruta esperada
10869:  8: 
10870:  9: - `agent`: `rag-azure-agent`
10871: 10: - `engine`: `Azure RAG Builder`
10872: 11: - `token_saver_profile`: `evidence-first`
10873: 12: - `caveman_profile`: `evidence-first` o `lite`
10874: 13: 
10875: 14: ## Validacion rapida
